high_descs: Turn around and go straight, then left around the sofas into the hallway, going all the way to the last door on the left, approaching the white dresser in the corner ahead.
Pick up the orange cup from atop the dresser.
Exit this room the way you came in and go back down the hallway until reaching the kitchen area on the left, approaching the fridge ahead.
Place the cup in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Turn around and look towards the dining table immediately ahead.
Place the cup down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Cool a cup in a fridge and place it on a dining table.

high_descs: Turn toward the sofa and go to the hallway beside the sofa, go to the last room on the right, and go to the dresser.
Pick up the orange cup from the dresser.
Go to the doorway and turn right, then go to the sofa and turn left and go across to the kitchen.
Place the cup in the fridge, then take the cup out of the fridge.
Turn around to the dining table.
Place the cup on the dining table to the right of the knife with the yellow handle.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled orange cup in on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the dresser.
Pick up cup from the dresser.
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the fridge.
Put cup inside the fridge then take it out.
Turn around and going straight, proceed to turn to the left towards the dining table.
Place cup on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Cooling the cup and placing it on the dining table.
